H.B. 312
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
Mar 5, 2025
SESSION 2025
HOUSE PRINCIPAL CLERK
H D
HOUSE BILL DRH10137-LGa-78
Short Title: Funds/Madison County Courthouse Relocation. (Public)
Sponsors: Representative Pless.
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS TO RELOCATE THE MADISON COUNTY
3 COURTHOUSE DAMAGED BY HURRICANE HELENE OUT OF THE FLOODPLAIN.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Office of State
6 Budget and Management the sum of eighty million dollars ($80,000,000) in nonrecurring funds
7 for the 2025-2026 fiscal year to provide a directed grant to Madison County to relocate the
8 Madison County Courthouse, which was severely damaged by Hurricane Helene, out of the
9 floodplain.
10 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
*DRH10137-LGa-78*

